
{{alias}}( id )
    Returns the package name associated with a provided error identifier prefix.

    Parameters
    ----------
    id: string
        Identifier prefix.

    Returns
    -------
    out: string|null
        Package name.

    Examples
    --------
    > var v = {{alias}}( 'Wiw' )
    '@stdlib/math/base/special/sin'
